@startuml 01-act-movie-search
title Movie Finder — Activity Diagram: Movie Search End-to-End Flow

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #EEF2FF
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #3D6DB5
skinparam ActivityFontSize 12
skinparam ActivityDiamondBackgroundColor #FFF9C4
skinparam ActivityDiamondBorderColor #F57F17
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFFDE7
skinparam NoteBorderColor #F9A825
skinparam PartitionBackgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam PartitionBorderColor #AAAAAA

|User (Browser)|
start
:Describe half-remembered film\nin natural language;
:Submit chat message (POST /chat);

|FastAPI Backend|
:Validate JWT bearer token;
if (Token valid?) then (no)
  :Return 401 Unauthorized;
  stop
else (yes)
endif
:Validate message length;
:Load or create session (PostgreSQL);
:Save user message to DB;
:Start LangGraph stream (stream_events());

|LangGraph Chain|
:Classify query intent (Claude Haiku);
:Embed query\n(EmbeddingProvider — injected singleton);
:Vector search in environment-scoped collection\n(Qdrant {env}_movies, top-K cosine);
:Parallel IMDb metadata fetch (async gather);
:Validate & rank candidates\n(deduplicate · confidence sort);

if (Enough high-confidence candidates?) then (no)
  :Request clarification from user;
  |FastAPI Backend|
  :Stream clarification event (SSE);
  |User (Browser)|
  :Receive clarification request;
  :Provide more detail;
  |LangGraph Chain|
else (yes)
endif

:Generate candidate list response (Claude Sonnet);
:Emit presentation chunks (SSE delta events);

|FastAPI Backend|
:Forward SSE chunks to browser;
:Save assistant message to DB;
:Update session phase → DISCOVERY;

|User (Browser)|
:Receive streaming response (EventSource tokens);
:Render candidate cards;

if (User confirms a movie?) then (yes)
  :Click confirm;
  |FastAPI Backend|
  :Update session phase → CONFIRMATION;
  :Store confirmed_movie as JSONB;
  |User (Browser)|
  :Receive confirmation & movie details;
  stop
else (no)
  :Refine with more detail;
  |LangGraph Chain|
endif

stop

@enduml
